00:00:52.970 --> 00:00:56.750
- I'm Waldo Martin, Professor
of History here at Cal

00:00:56.750 --> 00:01:01.440
and a member of the Jefferson
Memorial Lectures Committee.

00:01:01.440 --> 00:01:05.112
We're pleased, along with
